而世亦其得于公也。岂仅夸时荣一乡哉！吾于是作口：韶山苍苍，涧水泱泱，杜公之德，山高水长。\n\n\n\n邑口生口口张佩程拜撰文\n\n邑口口世口口口风拜书丹\n\n杜文强\n\n杜文□仝立\n\n杜士俊□口杰口口堂\n\n\n\n## 恩赐英耆杜公国桢德配王氏懿行碑杨\n\n公口廷口口口国桢口相德公之子也。伯仲四人。公居长，幼好儒书，年方弱冠，失怙，事慈母以孝，待兄弟以仁。但祖业微薄，糊口不给。十年以书代耕，多所诲成。壮年难辞公务，幸有伯舅岁进士树之郭公者，同心协力，办公有年，因之名闻乡曲、望重闾里。德配王氏，生子一文口女三，俱适名门；继配杨氏，生子三文宗光修女三，亦赴巨户。王氏早世。杨氏娴内则，勤织纺，鞠育有年，抚养之力至今不懈。公尔时经营家计，兼通商业，髦年书不释手，材艺济世之术，特其事。其教子也，负来且横经日用饮食，每示以稼穑艰难。公虽顾仓口勺口口夙兴，俾诸子披星戴月不蹈逸谚之习，\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_1347_659_1755_2427.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"20%\" /></div>\n", "isStart": false, "isEnd": true, "images": {"imgs/img_in_image_box_1347_659_1755_2427.jpg": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//9ee24971-2f61-4849-86e1-44c3fb02dcd5/markdown_0/imgs/img_in_image_box_1347_659_1755_2427.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A32%3A32Z%2F-1%2F%2F2cf77f24368875c5f88936c1a29fbde7286af12876c7805ed862cb14fb710821"}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//9ee24971-2f61-4849-86e1-44c3fb02dcd5/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A32%3A33Z%2F-1%2F%2F0c6017b9941037951aac7d83900568dc40c91e20ff731fdd85efd4d2711127dd", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//9ee24971-2f61-4849-86e1-44c3fb02dcd5/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A32%3A33Z%2F-1%2F%2Fc30cb558a9d7878b9a71ee7c88001420ae6f818de1dd3e038a0a411f3ca90f74", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//9ee24971-2f61-4849-86e1-44c3fb02dcd5/overall_ocr_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A32%3A34Z%2F-1%2F%2F815158761a3415ca1b108bf47915014aea81d286f1ae9593abb012b0b9cec668", "layout_order_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos